= Bytecode Optimizations =

= Operator Functions =

Useless but illustrative example

{{{
@OperatorFunction
boolean OR(boolean condition1, boolean condition2);
}}}

Usage:
{{{
if (condition1 OR condition2) { ... }
}}}

Effectivelly the same as:
{{{
if (OR(condition1, condition2)) { ... }
}}}

http://forums.java.net/jive/thread.jspa?threadID=132&tstart=0

